{"query": "To submit a delivery complaint, the customer should complete the Business Feedback Form on TelMart.com, select Delivery Complaints, and provide details such as order number, delivery date, and a description of the issue.", "category": "complaints_and_feedback", "file_name": "delivery_complaints.txt"}
{"query": "Alternatively, the customer may contact Customer Service by chat, call 1-400-840-4060, or email help@telmart.com to report a delivery issue.", "category": "complaints_and_feedback", "file_name": "delivery_complaints.txt"}

